window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In 2017, Devon Arthurs went from neo-Nazism to Islamic extremism, and he allegedly murdered his two roommates in defense of his new Muslim faith. In <i>Radicalized</i>, a seven-part docu-series, reporter Max Kutner investigates how Devon went from one extreme to another, shedding light on the online pathways to radicalization. He discovers maybe neo-Nazis &amp; jihadis have more in common than we think.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>This original podcast is seven episodes, please begin with the episode titled ‘Devon Arthurs.’ [Contains sensitive content]&nbsp;</p>"; 
